These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, disaster
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Hobby   | card-games | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
House: townhouse, modern
1. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5
2. the modern house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
3. the townhouse house is not to the right of the townhouse house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| House   | townhouse | modern |

 #################################

 
